{"tid":1287444,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足相信林慧韡(達犬)其實一直無變過?","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T15:24:48.000Z","uid":272077,"like":47,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b733075c0b0f66645b3e01f606d2a970f16226bd","tid":1287444,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"一直都係偽君子, 口講導人向善實際見錢開眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話自己張飛事實係無膽匪類, 連黃心穎個名都唔夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由好耐之前開始已經成日帶頭盔, 打機見到毋忘六四揮春都要話唔代表自己立場<br />\n聽落去嘻嘻哈哈好似講緊笑, 其實係虛偽, 好耐之前已經覺得錢比信念立場重要<br />\nbackup佬事件見多人支持佢就話&rdquo;既然好多人想我講咁我就講&rdquo;, 依家證明如果當初係一面倒屌佢佢肯定龜縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本佢一直都係冇腰骨嘅撚人一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n越嚟越少人同佢玩fifa(以前追逐生命,成龍個啲可能日久見人心)<br />\nbackup佬事件只不過backup佬更加仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0396646d1052f04f3185d62f5525ae11cae16a25","tid":1287444,"uid":15199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"變左<br />\n而家去左完美世界"},{"pid":"1541ad6b265b8ce6df612cebf3548128e0e7cef7","tid":1287444,"uid":64699,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbbcefffe87ea7a73dd998e96375890869a35d82","tid":1287444,"uid":85708,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"已經忘記達哥<br />\n點都好 俾黑警打的全部都係你的觀眾年齡層<br />\n而家佢地俾人打 俾人踩 <br />\n你都可以唔出聲<br />\n就算出返黎都唔再support<br />\n你點對班兄弟 大定睇到"},{"pid":"70c6f8c9b127e320f1fd6b159915cae82dafc6ac","tid":1287444,"uid":269148,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"一個windows都要用老翻嘅打機达人<br />\n你期望有啲咩風骨呀"},{"pid":"f733a59a0f33bb8f61512bee4bec9a3513f851a6","tid":1287444,"uid":2720